column6:
1- Choose USD - BTC pair and perform the transfer

2- After performing the transfer use the most commons crypto and perform different combinations as 

3- The source Account must be the from the account that ismaking the request 

4- The Payment method is related to the Account from Admin Panel that is making the request 

POST https://api.devwyre.com/v3/transfersAuthorization Bearer Token (account Secret Key){
     "source":"account:AC_QFY3BRDPW9E", 
     "sourceCurrency":"USD",
     "sourceAmount":100,
     "dest":"account:AC_uid OR wallet:WA_uid",
     "destCurrency":"BTC",
     "message": "USD to BTC test",
     "autoConfirm":true
}

column4:
1- User has to Download Postman

2- The user has to create an Account for Admin and NewDashboard

3- Configure Wallets

4- Add funds to the account

5- Perform a Login using https://admin.qawyre.com/ajax/core/v2/sessions/auth
   with body as: {"password":"Password","email":"Email","token":"7cc5acc81aa6e2807923b89ac25e90a8"}

6- From Response extract the session Id as: "sessionId": "38FEPFMAWT34DGCYEDVD9DN43J6ZENUG49DZWUFLQAE9D"

7- Go to the Request for transfers and perform the Action

8- From request, Login Use the Session-Id and Account 
           
           "authenticatedAs": "account:AC_xxxxxxxx",

           "sessionId": "Bx2X23RJGx2HND2YRNJBLFUUZTL3x7J9JYAQPCEAYT4B26x9VY"

1- User has to Download Postman

2- The user has to create an Account for Admin and New Dashboard

3- Configure Wallets

4- Add funds to the account

5- Perform a Login using https://admin.qawyre.com/ajax/core/v2/sessions/auth
   with body as: {"password":"Password","email":"Email","token":"7cc5acc81aa6e2807923b89ac25e90a8"}

6- From Response extract the session Id as: "sessionId": "38FEPFMAWT34DGCYEDVD9DN43J6ZENUG49DZWUFLQAE9D"

7- Go to the Request for transfers and perform the Action

8- From request, Login Use the Session-Id and Account 
           
           "authenticatedAs": "account:AC_xxxxxxxx",

           "sessionId": "Bx2X23RJGx2HND2YRNJBLFUUZTL3x7J9JYAQPCEAYT4B26x9VY"

2- After performing the transfer use the most commons crypto and perform different combinations as 

3- The source Account must be the from the account that ismaking the request 

4- The Payment method is related to the Account from Admin Panel that is making the request 

POST https://api.devwyre.com/v3/transfersAuthorization Bearer Token (account Secret Key){
     "source":"account:AC_QFY3BRDPW9E", 
     "sourceCurrency":"USD",
     "sourceAmount":100,
     "dest":"paymentMethod:PA_7RCEVBP9UPR",
     "destCurrency":"EUR",
     "message": "Sending the user payment method",
     "autoConfirm":true
}
